    <title>加入中国少年先锋队</title>
    <link href="http://daughter.tonybai.com/2017/10/20/become-member-of-china-young-pioneers/"/>
    <id>http://daughter.tonybai.com/2017/10/20/become-member-of-china-young-pioneers/</id>
    <published>2017-10-20T00:00:00.000Z</published>
    <updated>2017-10-21T15:07:17.000Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>今天是周五，也是我们这批二年级小学生正式加入中国少年先锋队的日子。一大早，我们就穿着整齐的校服来到学校。老师和家长代表为我们进行了简单的化妆，这是为了在入队仪式后的表演需要。</p>
<p>正式入队仪式举行，老师为我们佩戴上鲜艳的红领巾，我们高举右拳宣誓，大声朗读誓词，最后我们班所有同学一起表演了一个舞蹈，我是舞蹈最后那个举起红旗的小女孩哦。</p>
<p><img src="http://image.tonybai.com/img/201710/diary_20171020_1.jpg" alt="少先队入队1"><br><img src="http://image.tonybai.com/img/201710/diary_20171020_2.jpg" alt="少先队入队2"><br><img src="http://image.tonybai.com/img/201710/diary_20171020_3.jpg" alt="少先队入队3"><br><img src="http://image.tonybai.com/img/201710/diary_20171020_4.jpg" alt="少先队入队4"><br><img src="http://image.tonybai.com/img/201710/diary_20171020_5.jpg" alt="少先队入队5"><br><img src="http://image.tonybai.com/img/201710/diary_20171020_6.jpg" alt="少先队入队6"><br><img src="http://image.tonybai.com/img/201710/diary_20171020_7.jpg" alt="少先队入队7"></p>
